{"tid":1803983,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一月一遊行我會嗌：港獨都唔割！","createTime":"2019-12-30T15:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T16:54:38.000Z","uid":174512,"like":43,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b987a49de74f17bf979159f8c477a867d13a2c0a","tid":1803983,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港獨都唔割！</span></strong></span><br />\n中共咁耐以黎做咁多野都分化唔到和勇<br />\n但最近佢地搵到新路線<br />\n知道有好多年輕人支持港獨<br />\n同時亦有更多嘅人唔支持<br />\n於是派大量打手製造輿論分化我地<br />\n或者我地對港獨尚有分歧<br />\n但我地對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">滅共</span></span>早就二百萬合一<br />\n希望一月一有人會跟我一齊嗌：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港獨都唔割！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1ef419da22a358c3aa92edbe130c271cac0ca022","tid":1803983,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:36:12.000Z","msg":"推十野唔推"},{"pid":"8d238bd12f00b71fb915435435024f9b1d62e68c","tid":1803983,"uid":174512,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:36:37.000Z","msg":"香港獨立   唯一出路"},{"pid":"10a157909e38823a7ad39609fee3e9fba3e6301f","tid":1803983,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39afce19978becaa5c1b2b2ad2a814f070f2d793","tid":1803983,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:37:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"debbac3b3b8404553e7cb0287237a0e727d0f0ba","tid":1803983,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26448ea1c7d34de4494643f05c599f5f1ea629a5","tid":1803983,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:37:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de1c4e067508c82c56c063ee5eea69e800190954","tid":1803983,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:37: